type Booking {
  id: ID!
  kind: String
  start: String
  end: String
  user: User
  car: Car
  status: String
  office: Office
  createdAt: String
  updatedAt: String
}

type Car {
  id: ID!
  model: String
  make: String
  color: String
  year: Int
  price: Int
  description: String
  images: [String]
  createdAt: String
  updatedAt: String
}

type Office {
  id: ID!
  name: String
  address: String
  phone: String
  email: String
  images: [String]
  description: String
  latitude: Float
  longitude: Float
  createdAt: String
  updatedAt: String
}

type Query {
  bookings(filter: BookingFilterInput, pagination: PaginationInput): BookingsApiResult
  booking(id: ID!): BookingApiResult
  me: UserApiResult
  offices(pagination: PaginationInput): OfficesApiResult
  office(id: ID!): OfficeApiResult
  cars(pagination: PaginationInput): CarsApiResult
  car(id: ID!): CarApiResult
}

type User {
  id: ID!
  name: String!
  email: String!
  createdAt: String
  updatedAt: String
}
